[NPC] Londris: A shard of....
[NPC] Londris: Mortal.
[NPC] Londris: I do not have time for such nonsense.
[NPC] Londris: You have the audacity to ask something of our beloved goddess?
[NPC] Londris: Run back to whoever sent you.

[To] Oriven Thamal

[NPC Internal] Where can I get a shard of Dakkru's power?
[NPC] Oriven Thamal chuckles a bit.
[NPC] Oriven: Ah yes, the 'ol shard of Dakkru gag.
[NPC] Oriven: Another alchemist I presume?
[NPC] Oriven: First off, you don't take anything from Dakkru, She takes from you!
