[To] Sharven Xant-Areth

[NPC Internal] The curse is the shard of Dakkru's power?
[NPC] Sharven: Yes, I'm sorry if that was not clear.
[NPC] Sharven: But now you understand.
[NPC] Sharven: Now that you have cleansed your soul and emerged from the Death Realm, you have entered the whiteness stage of the Great Work.
[NPC] Sharven: I've sent the ingredients I've already made ahead to Vladovic.
[NPC] Sharven: Now quickly, before the curse expires, get to Ojaveda.
[NPC] Sharven: But instead of seeing Vladovic, go directly to Chired Idelall in Dsar Kore.
[NPC] Sharven: She should be waiting for you and can get the ingredient I've been looking for.
